                    <span>This book is about a young boy who is training to be a magician and a djinni named Bartemeus.This book is a tale that all will enjoy.If you like Harry Potter,you will like this.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Just fantastic</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
